  "english": [
    "<strong>GEMARA:</strong> It is stated in the mishna: This is <b>a stringency</b> of oaths vis-à-vis vows. The Gemara presumes that the mishna is referring to the distinction stated in previous <i>mishnayot</i> between saying: An offering that I will not eat of yours, and saying: An oath that I will not eat of yours. The Gemara asks: Should it be derived <b>by inference that</b> the statement: An offering that I will not eat of yours, <b>is</b> a valid <b>vow</b> by rabbinic law, and it is merely less stringent than the corresponding oath, which takes effect by Torah law? <b>But doesn’t</b> the mishna <b>teach</b> that it is <b>permitted</b> for him to eat, implying that the vow does not take effect at all?",
    "The Gemara answers: This <b>is taught with regard to the latter clause of the other section.</b> As opposed to a vow that is taken with regard to a matter that does not have actual substance, which takes effect only by rabbinic law, as articulated in the mishna (14b) and Gemara (15a), the subsequent mishna (15b) teaches that if someone says: <b>An oath that I will not sleep,</b> or: <b>That I will not speak,</b> or: <b>That I will not walk,</b> this activity is <b>forbidden</b> to him. It is concerning this contrast that the mishna says: <b>This is a stringency of oaths vis-à-vis vows.</b>",
    "§ It is stated in the mishna that there is <b>a stringency of vows vis-à-vis oaths. How so?</b> Whereas a vow can override a mitzva, an oath cannot. <b>Rav Kahana teaches</b> that <b>Rav Giddel said</b> that <b>Rav said, and Rav Tavyumei teaches</b> the same statement with a different attribution, i.e., <b>Rav Giddel said</b> that <b>Shmuel</b> said: <b>From where</b> is it derived <b>that one cannot take an oath to transgress the mitzvot? The verse states: “He shall not profane his word”</b> (Numbers 30:3). It is inferred that <b>his word,</b> i.e., the prohibition he accepted upon himself, <b>he shall not profane. However, he may profane</b> it <b>for the desires of Heaven.</b> If he took an oath to act against the will of God, the oath does not take effect.",
    "The Gemara asks: <b>What is different</b> about <b>a vow</b> that enables it to override mitzvot? Granted, <b>as it is written</b> in the Torah: <b>“When a man takes a vow to the Lord…he shall not profane his word”</b> (Numbers 30:3), which indicates that even with regard to matters that pertain to the Lord, i.e., mitzvot, one shall not profane his word, as the vow takes effect. However, with regard to <b>an oath it is also written</b> in the same verse: <b>“Or swears an oath” to God, “he shall not profane his word.”</b>",
    "<b>Abaye said:</b> The distinction is not between oaths and vows per se, but rather between the phraseology in each case. How so? <b>This</b> case, in which the prohibition overrides the mitzva, is referring to one <b>who said: The benefit</b> derived <b>from a <i>sukka</i></b> is hereby forbidden <b>to me.</b> Since the vow renders the <i>sukka</i> a forbidden object, it takes effect and overrides the mitzva, as one may not be fed what is forbidden to him, even if it is forbidden only to him. By contrast, <b>that</b> case, in which the prohibition does not take effect, is referring to one <b>who said:</b> I hereby take <b>an oath that I will not derive benefit from the <i>sukka</i>.</b> The oath does not take effect, as one is not entitled to take an oath to abstain from an act that he is obligated to perform.",
    "<b>Rava said</b> in objection to the explanation of Abaye: <b>But were mitzvot given for</b> the purpose of <b>deriving benefit?</b> The performance of mitzvot is not considered benefit. Why then would performance of the mitzva with the <i>sukka</i> be considered deriving benefit? <b>Rather, Rava said</b> a different explanation: <b>This</b> case is referring to one <b>who said: Dwelling in a <i>sukka</i></b> is hereby prohibited <b>to me, and that</b> case is referring to one <b>who said:</b> I hereby take <b>an oath that I will not dwell in a <i>sukka</i>.</b>",
    "§ The Gemara asks: <b>And</b> is the principle <b>that one cannot take an oath to transgress the mitzvot derived from here,</b> i.e., the above verse? <b>It is derived from there,</b> i.e., another verse, <b>as it is taught</b> in a <i>baraita</i>: One <b>might</b> have thought that if one <b>takes an oath to nullify a mitzva and does not nullify it,</b> one <b>might</b> have thought that <b>he will be liable</b> for violating an oath on a statement."
  ],
  "gemara": [
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"0\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><big><strong>גְּמָ׳</strong></big> ״חוֹמֶר״, מִכְּלָל דְּנֶדֶר הוּא. וְהָא ״מוּתָּר״ קָתָנֵי!",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"1\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אַסֵּיפָא דְּאִידַּךְ בָּבָא קָתָנֵי. ״שְׁבוּעָה שֶׁאֵינִי יָשֵׁן״,",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "״שֶׁאֵינִי מְדַבֵּר״, ״שֶׁאֵינִי מְהַלֵּךְ״ — אָסוּר. זֶה חוֹמֶר",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "בַּשְּׁבוּעוֹת מִבַּנְּדָרִים.<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"38\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span> <span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-steinsaltz\" data-sugya-kind=\"steinsaltz\" data-sugya-id=\"22\" data-sentence-id=\"2\">§</span> <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"2\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>חוֹמֶר בַּנְּדָרִים מִבַּשְּׁבוּעוֹת",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "כֵּיצַד כּוּ׳.<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"39\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span> <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Kahana, the brother of II, second-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2004\" data-full-name=\"Rav Kahana, the brother of II\" data-name-he=\"רב כהנא\">רַב כָּהֲנָא</span> מַתְנֵי: אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Giddel, second-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"820\" data-full-name=\"Rav Giddel\" data-name-he=\"רב גידל\">רַב גִּידֵּל</span> אָמַר",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"of Rav, first-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2578\" data-full-name=\"of Rav\" data-name-he=\"רב\">רַב</span>. <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Tavyumei, fifth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"1358\" data-full-name=\"Rav Tavyumei\" data-name-he=\"רב טביומי\">וְרַב טָבְיוֹמֵי</span> מַתְנֵי: אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Giddel, second-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"820\" data-full-name=\"Rav Giddel\" data-name-he=\"רב גידל\">רַב גִּידֵּל</span> אָמַר",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Shmuel II, first-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2763\" data-full-name=\"Shmuel II\" data-name-he=\"שמואל\">שְׁמוּאֵל</span>. מִנַּיִן שֶׁאֵין נִשְׁבָּעִין לַעֲבוֹר עַל",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "הַמִּצְוֹת? תַּלְמוּד לוֹמַר: ״לֹא יַחֵל דְּבָרוֹ״, ״דְּבָרוֹ לֹא יַחֵל״ —",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אֲבָל מֵיחֵל הוּא לְחֶפְצֵי שָׁמַיִם. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"3\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>מַאי שְׁנָא נֶדֶר —",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "דִּכְתִיב: ״אִישׁ כִּי יִדֹּר נֶדֶר לַה׳ ... לֹא יַחֵל דְּבָרוֹ״.",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "שְׁבוּעָה נָמֵי, הָא כְּתִיב: ״אוֹ הִשָּׁבַע שְׁבֻעָה לַה׳",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לֹא יַחֵל דְּבָרוֹ״! <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"4\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Abaye, fourth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"121\" data-full-name=\"Abaye\" data-name-he=\"אביי\">אַבָּיֵי</span>: הָא דְּאָמַר ״הֲנָאַת",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "סוּכָּה עָלַי״, הָא דְּאָמַר ״שְׁבוּעָה שֶׁלֹּא אֶהֱנֶה מִן",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "הַסּוּכָּה״. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"5\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabba I, fourth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2582\" data-full-name=\"Rabba I\" data-name-he=\"רבא\">רָבָא</span>: וְכִי מִצְוֹת לֵיהָנוֹת נִיתְּנוּ? אֶלָּא,",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabba I, fourth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2582\" data-full-name=\"Rabba I\" data-name-he=\"רבא\">רָבָא</span>: הָא דְּאָמַר ״יְשִׁיבַת סוּכָּה עָלַי״, וְהָא",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "דְּאָמַר ״שְׁבוּעָה שֶׁלֹּא אֵשֵׁב בַּסּוּכָּה״. <span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-steinsaltz\" data-sugya-kind=\"steinsaltz\" data-sugya-id=\"23\" data-sentence-id=\"6\">§</span> <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"6\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>וְשֶׁאֵין",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "נִשְׁבָּעִין לַעֲבוֹר עַל הַמִּצְוֹת מֵהָכָא נָפְקָא לֵיהּ?",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מֵהָתָם נָפְקָא לֵיהּ, דְּתַנְיָא: יָכוֹל נִשְׁבַּע לְבַטֵּל",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אֶת הַמִּצְוָה וְלֹא בִּיטֵּל, יָכוֹל יְהֵא חַיָּיב —",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    }
  ],
  "rashi": [
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">גמ&#x27;</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">מדקאמר</span> חוֹמֶר בַּשְּׁבוּעוֹת מִבַּנְּדָרִים.</b> כלומר דזה חומר טפי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "בשבועות מחומרא דנדרים מכלל דנדר מיהא הוי כי אמר קרבן",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "לא אוכל לך וכו' דאיסור נדר איכא מדרבנן אלא דלא לקי מדאורייתא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ולא מיחייב קרבן שבועה כי היכי דמחייב בשבועות: <b>וְהָא ״מוּתָּר״</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:1:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>קָתָנֵי</b> בנדרים דאפילו שום איסור",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:1:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ליכא: <b>אַסֵּיפָא.</b> הא דקתני חומר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "בשבועות מבנדרים דמשמע דנדר חשיב",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "לא קאי ארישא דקתני קרבן לא אוכל לך",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "אלא אסיפא דאידך בבא (<a href=\"/nedarim/14b\">לעיל נדרים יד:</a>)",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "דקתני קונם שאיני ישן שאיני מדבר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "הרי זה בלא יחל דברו ואומר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "רבינא עלה לעיל (<a href=\"/nedarim/15a\">נדרים טו.</a>) לעולם כדקתני",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "שאני ישן ומאי בל יחל בל יחל דרבנן",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "דהיינו איסור דרבנן אבל שבועה שאיני",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ישן שאיני מדבר מדאורייתא אסור",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "וזה חומר בשבועות מבנדרים ששבועה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "חלה על דבר שאין בו ממש וחייב",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "קרבן מה שאין כן בנדרים: <b>אֲבָל</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>מֵיחֵל הוּא לְחֶפְצֵי שָׁמַיִם.</b> שאם נדר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "לעבור על אחת מן המצות אין שבועה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "חלה עליו ומיחל לאותה שבועה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "דמושבע ועומד הוא לקיימה ואין",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "שבועה חלה עליו ויכול לחלל דברו:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>מַאי שְׁנָא נֶדֶר.</b> דאמר כי נדר על",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "המצוה חל עליו הנדר וכי עבר ועשה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "המצוה קם ליה בלא יחל: <b>דִּכְתִיב: כִּי</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">ידור</span> נֶדֶר לַה׳</b> דאפילו בחפצי שמים",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "דלה' לא יחל דברו: <b>שְׁבוּעָה נָמֵי</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:4:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "תחול עליה אם נשבע לעבור על המצוה: <b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">והכתיב</span> נָמֵי, ״אוֹ</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:4:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>הִשָּׁבַע <span class=\"dh-divergent\">שבועה</span> לַה׳ לֹא יַחֵל דְּבָרוֹ״</b> דלה' סמוך אאו השבע דמשמע",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:4:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "נמי לה' השבע שבועה לא יחל דברו: <b>אָמַר <span class=\"dh-divergent\">אביי</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">הא</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">דאמר</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">הנאת</span></b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:4:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">סוכה</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">עלי</span> הָא <span class=\"dh-divergent\">דאמר</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">שבועה</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">שלא</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">אהנה</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">מן</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">הסוכה</span>.</b> כלומר הא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:4:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "דקתני מתניתין שנודרין על המצוה כגון דאמר הנאת סוכה עלי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:4:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "דהשתא קאסר חפצא עליה דהכי מצי למידר אפי' לכתחילה כדאמרינן",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:4:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "לעיל אע\"ג דמשועבד לאשתו בתשמיש חל עליו הנדר כי אמר הנאת",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:4:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "תשמישך עלי שאינו אוסר עצמו עליה אלא לדידה אוסר עליו",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:4:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "וקסבר אביי דבכל לשון שבועה לא מצינו דתיחול עליה דאי אמר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:4:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "שבועה הנאת סוכה עלי דהנאתה אוסר עליו דהא ודאי לא הויא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:4:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "שבועה אלא נדר דכיון דקאמר עלי היינו נדר דכל היכא דקאמר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:4:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "עלי אמרינן היינו נדר וחייב באחריותו ונדר הוא כי אמר הכי אפילו",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:4:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "לכתחלה מצי נדר וקאסר חפצא עליה אבל שבועה לא מצי לאוקמי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:4:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "אלא כגון דאמר שבועה שלא אהנה וכהאי גוונא לא חייל עליה דלא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:4:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "מצי למיסר נפשיה עליה דמצוה כי קאמר שלא אהנה דאוסר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:4:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "עצמו במצוה שהוא משועבד לו וכה\"ג מיירי חומר בנדרים מבשבועות",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:4:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "דבנדרים אומר קונם הנאת סוכה עלי ובשבועה שלא אהנה: <b>וְכִי</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:6:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>מִצְוֹת לֵיהָנוֹת נִיתְּנוּ.</b> דקאמר הנאת סוכה עלי הא לא ליהנות ניתנו",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:6:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ולא מצי למיסר נפשיה בהנאתה דהא לא חשיבה הנאה מצוה דלא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:6:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ניתנו בשביל הנאה: <b>אֶלָּא, אָמַר רָבָא: <span class=\"dh-divergent\">וכו&#x27;</span> ״יְשִׁיבַת סוּכָּה עָלַי״</b> כדאמרן",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:6:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "דבישיבת סוכה עלי קאסר חפצא עליה: <b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">ובשבועה</span> שֶׁלֹּא אֵשֵׁב.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:6:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "קאסר נפשיה מן חפצא והא לא מצי למיעבד דמשועבד הוא למצוה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:6:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ולהכי לא חיילא עליה שבועה: <b>יָכוֹל יְהֵא חַיָּיב.</b> קרבן שבועה:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 16b:7:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    }
  ],
  "vilna_piskaot": [
